Name: LineArt Jigsaw Puzzle - Erotica 4
About the game: Nice 6 x 6 jigsaw puzzle featuring soft erotica/lesbian line drawings of sexy women in panties by LineArtBabe, on a smooth luxury graphical background. Relaxing background music. The game features 12 puzzles which you can solve in any order of your choice. The game is a bit more challenging as all puzzles are line art based and a bit more difficult. There is no time limit, but there is a timer in case you want to see how quickly you can solve each puzzle.
